#: org.kde.linux.metainfo.xml:9
msgid ""
"A modern Linux distribution focused on the KDE Plasma desktop environment"
msgstr ""
"Arreta KDE Plasma mahaigain ingurunean jartzen duen Linux banaketa moderno "
"bat"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.linux.metainfo.xml:14
msgid ""
"KDE Linux is a user-friendly operating system built around the KDE Plasma "
"desktop environment. It provides a complete computing experience with a "
"focus on productivity, customization, and ease of use."
msgstr ""
"KDE Linux, KDE Plasma mahaigain ingurunearen inguruan eraikita dagoen "
"sistema eragile lagunkoi bat da. Konputazio esperientzia osoa eskaintzen du, "
"arreta produktibitatean, pertsonalizazioan, eta erabiltzeko erraztasunean "
"jarriz."

